title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Halo Infinite Pelican - available for MSFS
description:
In this video we will look at the Halo Infinite Pelican aircraft which has been made available for free just a few hours ago. We will start with installing the aircraft and having a look at the liveries. After that we will review the interior and exterior and take the aircraft out for a flight.
